1
00:00:58,719 --> 00:00:59,520
Money

2
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:02,679
I've got the money

3
00:01:03,399 --> 00:01:05,319
I guarantee no one will find the body

4
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,959
The most valuable thing in this world...

5
00:01:14,959 --> 00:01:17,280
...and the easiest capital to acquire is people

6
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:20,680
You really didn't let me down

7
00:01:28,359 --> 00:01:31,400
My brother used that money to buy this land

8
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:39,159
I'm going to build my empire right here

9
00:01:53,439 --> 00:01:55,959
So they were all in cahoots

10
00:01:57,719 --> 00:01:59,560
They are the biggest criminal syndicate

11
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,439
Engaging in a business that devours people

12
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:03,799
Their hands

13
00:02:03,799 --> 00:02:05,719
are all stained with the blood of innocent victims

14
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,240
Inspector Qi

15
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:09,280
So

16
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:12,159
what roles did A Si and Fang Qiu

17
00:02:12,719 --> 00:02:13,919
play in the real story?

18
00:02:17,599 --> 00:02:19,960
A Si's story is mostly as she told it

19
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,280
But she still held some things back

20
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,439
Here, Sister Man, test the water

21
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:25,800
Mmh

22
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:26,639
It's good

23
00:02:30,039 --> 00:02:30,840
Sister Man

24
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:31,919
To be honest

25
00:02:31,919 --> 00:02:32,960
I really envy you

26
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:36,319
You have money to spend

27
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:38,479
and your life is so free and easy

28
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:39,719
You can too

29
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:40,520
Me?

30
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,159
Yeah

31
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,879
How could I?

32
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,479
I'm just not destined for a life of luxury

33
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:45,800
A Si

34
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:46,639
You...

35
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:47,680
should take advantage of your youth

36
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,360
and go out to see the world

37
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:51,319
I don't know how to do anything

38
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:52,800
What could I do out there?

39
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:54,039
Silly girl

40
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:57,080
Youth and beauty are a woman's greatest capital

41
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:57,680
You know?

42
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:58,960
You can't waste it

43
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:01,360
If you wait until you're old and faded

44
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,919
who will even spare you a glance?

45
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,280
Listen to Sis

46
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:05,639
Don't waste yourself in

47
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:07,000
this hopeless place

48
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:10,039
Look

49
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:13,680
How much money can you make in a year now?

50
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:15,639
Not much

51
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,439
A Si

52
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:22,599
You...

53
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:25,159
think about going out there

54
00:03:25,159 --> 00:03:26,919
There are tons of chances to make money

55
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:30,360
Call me when you've thought it through

56
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,000
Sis will arrange it for you

57
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,520
Go out there

58
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:35,080
The sky is the limit

59
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,159
Thank you, Sis

60
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:52,840
Youth and beauty are a woman's greatest capital

61
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:53,639
You know?

62
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:54,919
It shouldn't be wasted

63
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,199
Once you've decided

64
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,319
give me a call

65
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:13,639
They are pitiful people who, after falling into hell,

66
00:04:15,159 --> 00:04:16,759
turned into demons

67
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,000
Come on, girls, get off the bus

68
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:23,240
Go check in

69
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:26,160
Authentic Tai Cheng cola!

70
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:27,920
Try some!

71
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:28,759
Brother

72
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,720
Um, after we check in later

73
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,879
can we go out for a stroll?

74
00:04:32,199 --> 00:04:32,600
Sure

75
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:34,040
We have free time today

76
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,279
Tomorrow we'll go to the factory for orientation

77
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:42,720
Authentic Tai Cheng snacks!

78
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,120
Such beautiful steamed dumplings!

79
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,759
Authentic snacks!

80
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,800
Buy two, get one free!

81
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,319
Come and take a look!

82
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,639
Where is this?

83
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,199
Let me out!

84
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:11,560
Let me out!

85
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,160
Who was screaming just now?

86
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,079
It was you, huh?

87
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:30,600
You have to know the rules when you get here

88
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,399
Otherwise

89
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,759
this is what happens

90
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,720
Do you understand?

91
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:55,480
I'm a man who rewards and punishes fairly.

92
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,000
As long as your performance meets the target,

93
00:05:58,399 --> 00:06:00,279
then a promotion and raise are guaranteed.

94
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,079
But if your performance is poor,

95
00:06:06,199 --> 00:06:07,399
then don't blame me.

96
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,600
After all, we don't keep freeloaders here.

97
00:06:11,279 --> 00:06:11,759
Do you understand?

98
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:17,079
Boss Shan is asking you!

99
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,439
Answer loudly!

100
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,800
Do you understand?

101
00:06:20,839 --> 00:06:21,720
Understood.

102
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:27,199
Weren't you screaming loud enough last night?

103
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:32,199
Why aren't you talking now?

104
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,240
Do you understand?

105
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,639
Do you understand?

106
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:37,439
Speak up! Alright, alright.

107
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,560
Come on, speak up.

108
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:39,800
Come back.

109
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:46,120
Can't have her face getting scratched up.

110
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,240
We're counting on it to make money.

111
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,439
Since you're here, you might as well accept it.

112
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,040
As long as you work hard,

113
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,959
then you can definitely

114
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:06,000
create a beautiful future for yourself.

115
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:07,480
Do you understand?

116
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,279
Yes, yes.

117
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,199
I won't.

118
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,279
Where did you get the cigarettes?

119
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:27,600
I asked for them.

120
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,240
Are you resigned to this?

121
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:38,319
What else can I do?

122
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,040
We're going to die sooner or later anyway.

123
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:43,160
Might as well take a chance.

124
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:44,839
I know.

125
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:46,600
You definitely want to get out.

126
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,040
Right?

127
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,040
Wanting to and being able to are two different things.

128
00:07:55,399 --> 00:07:56,199
Before,

129
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:59,120
I always wanted to be a rich wife.

130
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,279
But now?

131
00:08:05,959 --> 00:08:07,439
As long as we're alive, there's hope.

132
00:08:08,439 --> 00:08:09,319
Who knows?

133
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:11,319
Maybe a miracle will happen.

134
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,279
As long as I can escape,

135
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,079
I absolutely won't hesitate.

136
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,079
What do you plan to do?

137
00:08:24,439 --> 00:08:25,600
Chen Xiaoyun

138
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:27,879
is planning to escape.

139
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,360
Yes.

140
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,439
Tonight.

141
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:33,960
Why did you turn me in?

142
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:36,440
You said it yourself.

143
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:39,200
As long as you can demonstrate your value,

144
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:42,000
you can create a beautiful future for yourself.

145
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:43,600
I...

146
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:45,399
I'm willing to do anything for you.
